Q: 总结在17th Of September的所有航班中，最常使用的前三飞机型号及其座位数（取区间）。
SQL:
SELECT
    b.aircraft_model_name,
    COUNT(*) AS num,
    MAX(b.seat_num) AS max_seat_num,
    MIN(b.seat_num) AS min_seat_num
FROM
    zts_plane_flight a
JOIN
    aircraft_details b ON a.pure_reg = b.pure_reg
WHERE
    (a.dep_icao = "FNBG" OR a.arr_icao = "FNBG")
GROUP BY
    b.aircraft_model_name
ORDER BY
    num DESC
LIMIT 3;

    b.aircraft_model_name,
    COUNT(*) AS num,
    MAX(b.seat_num) AS max_seat_num,
    MIN(b.seat_num) AS min_seat_num
FROM
    zts_plane_flight a
JOIN
    aircraft_details b ON a.pure_reg = b.pure_reg
WHERE
    (a.dep_icao = "EKYT" OR a.arr_icao = "EKYT")
GROUP BY
    b.aircraft_model_name
ORDER BY
    num DESC
LIMIT 3;

    b.aircraft_model_name,
    COUNT(*) AS num,
    MAX(b.seat_num) AS max_seat_num,
    MIN(b.seat_num) AS min_seat_num
FROM
    zts_plane_flight a
JOIN
    aircraft_details b ON a.pure_reg = b.pure_reg
WHERE
    (a.dep_icao = "EGFA" OR a.arr_icao = "EGFA")
GROUP BY
    b.aircraft_model_name
ORDER BY
    num DESC
LIMIT 3;
